LE at checkout, you&#8217;ll get an additional 15% off your total. This is the cheapest you&#8217;ll be able to pick up PvP books and shirts all year. So don&#8217;t let the opportunity slip past you. If you have friends or family that you think would enjoy reading PvP, here&#8217;s your chance to get some of your Christmas shopping done early and save some bucks.</p><p>Visit the PvP store at <a href=\"http://www.pvpstuff.com\">PVPSTUFF.COM</a></p><p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-Xsi6gQhQZjpBusUO3ohqIqQMis/0/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-Xsi6gQhQZjpBusUO3ohqIqQMis/0/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a><br/><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-Xsi6gQhQZjpBusUO3ohqIqQMis/1/da\"><img src=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/-Xsi6gQhQZjpBusUO3ohqIqQMis/1/di\" border=\"0\" ismap=\"true\"></img></a></p><img src=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/Pvponline/~4/55iab5xR1zg\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\"/>") (wfw:commentRss nil "http://www.pvponline.com/2010/10/27/pvp-store-fire-sale/feed/") (slash:comments nil "0") (feedburner:origLink nil "http://www.pvponline.com/2010/10/27/pvp-store-fire-sale/")) (item nil (title nil "Boo-ring!") (link nil "http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/Pvponline/~3/tyjETXBB5mM/") (comments nil "http://www.pvponline.com/2010/10/27/boo-ring/#comments") (pubDate nil "Wed, 27 Oct 2010 05:00:41 +0000") (dc:creator nil "admin") (category nil "comic") (guid ((isPermaLink . "false")) "http://www.pvponline.com/?p=6013") (description nil "	<p><a href=\"http://www.pvponline.com/2010/10/27/boo-ring/\"><img src=\"http://www.pvponline.com/comics/pvp20101027.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Boo-ring!\" title=\"Boo-ring!\" /></a></p>") (content:encoded nil "	<p><a href=\"http://www.pvponline.com/2010/10/27/boo-ring/\"><img src=\"http://www.pvponline.com/comics/pvp20101027.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"Boo-ring!\" title=\"Boo-ring!\" /></a></p><p><a href=\"http://feedads.g.doubleclick.net/~a/3mmIbHlx2l4CeCG8TA8TrSxjRnE/0/da\"><img 